Je396Ev-dvAvl3ei-O0EIg
You can't come here and not compare it to the o.g. Boiling Crab. Whether the owners like to admit it or not, it's pretty much an exact replica...and that's not a bad thing.  I've been craving this kind of food so badly since moving to AZ and finally got a chance to hit up the Angry Crab. The food is awesome. Spray ketchup on the table and eat with your hands while butter, garlic, and grease slop all over your face. Not an ounce of shame. Flavors are perfect. Food is hot. Spice levels are SPICY. Shrimp were large and not overcooked. Fries are perfectly crisp. Blue crab is kind of hard to eat but if you like crab guts and like to work for your food, it's worth it. Crawfish was sold out when I went so I can't comment on quality. I hope they don't raise their prices and somehow keep the 2-3 hour BC waits away. Shout out to our server Michelle, who was great and full of energy on a busy day. Protip: the sauce here is great bowel care, if you get what I mean.

